    <p class="text-lg text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 mb-8 leading-relaxed">Estimate the color of your beer in SRM (Standard Reference Method) and EBC from your malt bill. Uses the Morey equation, the most widely accepted homebrew color model.</p>

